title: Korres Wild Rose Mineral Foundation, Fair, 0.26 Ounce
description: This talc-free, loose powder foundation contains brightening wild rose extract.

title: Acne.org 16 oz. Cleanser
description: When treating acne, it is important to avoid irritation. This generously sized 16 oz. ultra-gentle liquid Cleanser is carefully designed with only the gentlest cleansing ingredients to be pH balanced so it doesn't overdry or strip the skin. It also produces a thick lather which cleanses just the right amount and rinses clean.This Cleanser was developed specifically for use with The Regimen (acne.org/regimen) but can also be used as a stand-alone cleanser for all skin types.

title: Trader Joe's Tea Tree Tingle Shampoo with Peppermint, Tea Tree and Eucalyptus Botanicals, 16-Ounces
description: We've worked with an upscale boutique to bring you this salon-quality shampoo that will rejuvenate your hair with its refreshing tingle. A blend of certified organic botanicals including peppermint and tea tree work together to moisturize and clarify your hair while alleviating dry scalp. Our product contains no laurel/laureth sulfates found in most shampoos and is suitable for all hair types.
